{"tid":176802,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[餓撚入一入黎]元朗！燒味既福地","createTime":"2017-03-28T11:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T13:53:24.000Z","uid":38758,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"516ad0a66194e81675ec3c6d8d8fa0b960dcffbc","tid":176802,"uid":38758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:52:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的頭先收工一落車諗唔到食咩，<br />\n是但去間燒味鋪，一埋位就用老練既口吻<br />\n老闆比個鴨飯呀！師傅用快過我打飛機高速咁斬好盒鴨飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/28/193923_23a9e1efdaa8b2271c3c7232c7a9d959.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F28%2F193923_23a9e1efdaa8b2271c3c7232c7a9d959.jpg&h=b2183481&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一睇到嘩！脾呀，正<br />\n正當我比完張紅衫魚出黎，老闆就問我有無兩蚊<br />\n咁岩有，未行過方便比埋老闆，找贖完數下啦<br />\n4張20蚊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁即刻問老闆有無找錯啦<br />\n老闆就用冷淡既語氣同我講「岩呀廿二蚊喳嘛」<br />\n喳嘛？廿二蚊你比脾我食‼️<br />\n我想講既係今日窮撚好快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eff86cf5c51cf9b36038e20ffb4e0a25978e1a3","tid":176802,"uid":1707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T11:56:09.000Z","msg":"仲要咁大份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192f38c2b6de435a43e37bff1af9e53039b30199","tid":176802,"uid":38758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T12:01:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲要咁大份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n這些機會"},{"pid":"5264d1747ca369deca0a44277cb00ffc9b0d481b","tid":176802,"uid":25213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T12:16:55.000Z","msg":"廿蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9697b53ccafe3caa3675bb13ea2fac57cbfaa8f","tid":176802,"uid":25213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T12:17:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廿蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊間？"},{"pid":"e785343c306c02a1619ad4a6aeb5bfe9fc0dc658","tid":176802,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T12:23:44.000Z","msg":"元朗大同餅店隔離嗰間D燒肉幾脆，個例湯幾好飲，大榮華隔離嗰間就好多人排隊，四季食過就一般啦，乳豬大王真係得乳豬好食，天鴻D鵝飯好多骨冇肉食，大橋街市後面果兩間好污糟"},{"pid":"458bdb9c0d31d283387e8b8f73d2f116df1f43ca","tid":176802,"uid":3594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:25:05.000Z","msg":"元朗的話忠輝好食"},{"pid":"6afa9f936b889f2f9627abd61975275bd03c9975","tid":176802,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:28:01.000Z","msg":"元朗人傑地靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9042e99fac82d449a15f413d38b9959722c4990","tid":176802,"uid":54832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T05:49:11.000Z","msg":"金記"},{"pid":"e818e8a36a542be2ff9d518b1b9096d9d29862af","tid":176802,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201